Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:55.20,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}para deshacerme de mis preocupaciones
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.66,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}Estoy minimizando el aleteo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.50,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}que siento este Abril
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.37,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}Éramos niños pequeños felices,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.01,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}llenos de curiosidad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:12.05,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}Yo fui quién te empujó hacia adelante
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:17.89,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}Vamos a escapar de nuestros límites
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:23.44,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}y pararnos en el camino
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:30.92,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}Vamos a ir en bici hasta muy lejos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:36.29,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)} Vamos a llevar nuestras esperanzas y sueños en la cesta
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:43.50,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}El futuro del que hemos hablado parece bonito
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:49.27,ED HnF,,0,0,0,avoid,{\blur2\fad(250,200)}La sombra crece, y no nos enteramos de nada.
